[{"client_msg_id":"ac377e20-9128-4a85-9af3-b3ece1ff0299","type":"message","text":"How can I modify (e.g., double) some elements in an array?\n```A = 1:4\nA[2:3] = 2 * A[2:3]```","user":"ULA88TKUY","ts":"1612547133.174900","team":"T68168MUP","blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"sl1TA","elements":[{"type":"rich_text_section","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"How can I modify (e.g., double) some elements in an array?\n"}]},{"type":"rich_text_preformatted","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"A = 1:4\nA[2:3] = 2 * A[2:3]"}]}]}],"thread_ts":"1612547133.174900","reply_count":15,"reply_users_count":4,"latest_reply":"1612548439.178800","reply_users":["UM30MT6RF","U7HAYKY9X","UDB26738Q","ULA88TKUY"],"subscribed":false},{"client_msg_id":"886ee611-6765-486d-ad94-6f9a8672e3d2","type":"message","text":"Probably something like `view(A, 2:3) .*= 2`","user":"UM30MT6RF","ts":"1612547193.175000","team":"T68168MUP","blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"QjM1E","elements":[{"type":"rich_text_section","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Probably something like "},{"type":"text","text":"view(A, 2:3) .*= 2","style":{"code":true}}]}]}],"thread_ts":"1612547133.174900","parent_user_id":"ULA88TKUY"},{"client_msg_id":"e28f1947-2576-48a4-acb2-845112acd739","type":"message","text":"Not all array-like types can be changed. `1:4` is an `AbstractArray`  of type `UnitRange{Int}` , which are not mutable.","user":"U7HAYKY9X","ts":"1612547202.175200","team":"T68168MUP","blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"RQ0","elements":[{"type":"rich_text_section","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Not all array-like types can be changed. "},{"type":"text","text":"1:4","style":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" is an "},{"type":"text","text":"AbstractArray","style":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":"  of type "},{"type":"text","text":"UnitRange{Int}","style":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" , which are not mutable."}]}]}],"thread_ts":"1612547133.174900","parent_user_id":"ULA88TKUY","reactions":[{"name":"+1","users":["ULA88TKUY"],"count":1}]},{"client_msg_id":"65ec6dc9-b577-4002-b3ee-5d57afdba613","type":"message","text":"your `A` isn't a mutable array, it's a special data structure for range","user":"UDB26738Q","ts":"1612547203.175400","team":"T68168MUP","blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"puW","elements":[{"type":"rich_text_section","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"your "},{"type":"text","text":"A","style":{"code":true}},{"type":"text","text":" isn't a mutable array, it's a special data structure for range"}]}]}],"thread_ts":"1612547133.174900","parent_user_id":"ULA88TKUY","reactions":[{"name":"point_up","users":["UM30MT6RF","UH8A351DJ"],"count":2}]},{"client_msg_id":"2c98adde-dac4-4141-ad55-8866fe1a4108","type":"message","text":"```julia&gt; A = collect(1:4)\n4-element Vector{Int64}:\n 1\n 2\n 3\n 4\n\njulia&gt; A[2:3] .*= 2\n2-element view(::Vector{Int64}, 2:3) with eltype Int64:\n 4\n 6\n\njulia&gt; A\n4-element Vector{Int64}:\n 1\n 4\n 6\n 4```","user":"UDB26738Q","ts":"1612547255.175700","team":"T68168MUP","blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"R/P=W","elements":[{"type":"rich_text_preformatted","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"julia> A = collect(1:4)\n4-element Vector{Int64}:\n 1\n 2\n 3\n 4\n\njulia> A[2:3] .*= 2\n2-element view(::Vector{Int64}, 2:3) with eltype Int64:\n 4\n 6\n\njulia> A\n4-element Vector{Int64}:\n 1\n 4\n 6\n 4"}]}]}],"thread_ts":"1612547133.174900","parent_user_id":"ULA88TKUY","reactions":[{"name":"+1","users":["ULA88TKUY"],"count":1}]},{"client_msg_id":"0351a0ce-1812-4cc5-a73d-9d08875de342","type":"message","text":"&gt; `A[2:3] .*= 2`\nNote that this will allocate `A[2:3]` once","user":"UM30MT6RF","ts":"1612547306.176100","team":"T68168MUP","blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"yKI1Y","elements":[{"type":"rich_text_quote","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"A[2:3] .*= 2","style":{"code":true}}]},{"type":"rich_text_section","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"\nNote that this will allocate "},{"type":"text","tex